
  <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 user_input">
    <%= form_tag(funds_path, method: "post", remote: true, id: "nl-form", class: "nl-form clearfix") do %>
      I am currently <input type="text" value="" placeholder="35" name="age" id="age-input" />
      <div class="nl-overlay"></div>
      . I have $
        <input type="text" value="" placeholder="10,000" name="present_value" id="pv-input"/>
      <div class="nl-overlay"></div>
      saved for retirement. I make monthly investments of $
        <input type="text" value="" placeholder="1,000" name="pmt" id="cont-input" />
      <div class="nl-overlay"></div>
      and my high-fee mutual fund's ticker symbol is 
        <input type="text" value="" placeholder="FFFFX" name="fund_ticker" />
      .
      <div class="nl-submit-wrap col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <button class="nl-submit submit center" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#myModal" type="submit">My Broker can buy</button>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <div id="explain-footer" class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
      <p>We assumed that you would retire at 65 and your portfolio would grow at 8% a year, before expenses. We compared your portfolio against <%= link_to "this one", "https://personal.vanguard.com/us/funds/snapshot?FundId=0695&FundIntExt=INT" %>, which has an expense ratio of 0.17%.</p>
      <p>Made with love at the Flatiron School</p>
    </div>

<div class="modal fade" id="myModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
        <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Here's what your broker can now buy...</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
            <!-- <div class="monopoly_man"></div> -->
      </div>
